    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>えいごで:</strong> The weather is getting colder this week, including some snow!</p>

<p><strong>Japanese:</strong> こんしゅうてんきがさむくなった、ゆきふった。</p>

<p><a href="http://www.smugmug.com/photos/i-ZFMSFz7/0/O/i-ZFMSFz7.jpg"><img class="center" src="http://www.smugmug.com/photos/i-ZFMSFz7/0/X2/i-ZFMSFz7-X2.jpg"></a></p>

